OL,3,CAir Ambulance relocates to new #3.6m
OL,4,Cairport base
OL,6,FHampshire and Isle of Wight Air
OL,7,FAmbulance has completed a move to its
OL,8,Fnew #3.6 million airbase.
OL,10,FThe service has relocated from its old
OL,11,Fheadquarters in Andover to a state-of-
OL,12,Fthe-art facility at Southampton
OL,13,FAirport.
OL,15,FIt said the move was needed so that it
OL,16,Fcould be closer to more densely
OL,17,Fpopulated cities, including
OL,18,FWinchester, Southampton and Portsmouth.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
