OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1781097082
OL,3,CAir Ambulance relocates to new #3.6m
OL,4,Cairport base
OL,6,FData had shown that a majority (70%)
OL,7,Fof the emergencies it attended were in
OL,8,Fthese areas.
OL,10,FCrews are now reaching patients "far
OL,11,Fquicker than ever before", the service
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,19,FThe money to buy the two-storey
OL,20,Ffacility was raised through donations
OL,21,Ffrom more than 13,000 people.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
