OL,3,CAir Ambulance relocates to new #3.6m
OL,4,Cairport base
OL,6,FIt features a helicopter hanger,
OL,7,Fhelipad, training rooms and on-site
OL,8,Faccommodation.
OL,10,FHampshire and Isle of Wight Air
OL,11,FAmbulance CEO, Richard Corbett hailed
OL,12,Fthe opening as a "monumental occasion".
OL,14,F"The support we have received from
OL,15,Fmembers of the public, businesses,
OL,16,Forganisations, community groups,
OL,17,Ftrusts and foundations has been
OL,18,Fastonishing," he said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
