OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1781097082
OL,3,CAir Ambulance relocates to new #3.6m
OL,4,Cairport base
OL,6,F"I am incredibly grateful to each
OL,7,Fsupporter, volunteer, crew member and
OL,8,Fcolleague for their dedication in
OL,9,Forchestrating this move.
OL,11,F"It has been a tremendous effort while
OL,12,Falso focusing on our primary mission
OL,13,Fof bringing exceptional critical care
OL,14,Fto people in Hampshire and the Isle of
OL,15,FWight."
